  "text": "Every night at 2:13 AM, my baby monitor whispered the same sentence: ‘Daddy, come downstairs.’ The first night, I laughed it off. The second night, I unplugged the monitor. The third night, it turned on by itself. 'Daddy, come downstairs.' This time, the voice sounded closer. I grabbed a kitchen knife and walked to the stairs. At the bottom, I saw a little girl standing in the hallway, holding the baby monitor. She smiled at me. Then the monitor in her hand crackled. And my own voice came through it. 'Don’t go near her.' I looked down. My phone lit up with a calendar reminder I had never made: 2:14 AM — Wake up. You forgot you died here.",
  "segments": [
    {
      "startSeconds": 0,
      "endSeconds": 5.92,
      "text": "Every night at 2:13 AM, my baby monitor whispered the same sentence: ‘Daddy, come downstairs.’"
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 5.92,
      "endSeconds": 9.56,
      "text": "The first night, I laughed it off. The second night, I unplugged the monitor."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 9.56,
      "endSeconds": 13.08,
      "text": "The third night, it turned on by itself. 'Daddy, come downstairs.'"
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 13.08,
      "endSeconds": 17.16,
      "text": "This time, the voice sounded closer. I grabbed a kitchen knife and walked to the stairs."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 17.16,
      "endSeconds": 21.88,
      "text": "At the bottom, I saw a little girl standing in the hallway, holding the baby monitor. She smiled at me."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 21.88,
      "endSeconds": 26.16,
      "text": "Then the monitor in her hand crackled. And my own voice came through it. 'Don’t go near her.'"
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 26.16,
      "endSeconds": 32.8,
      "text": "I looked down. My phone lit up with a calendar reminder I had never made: 2:14 AM — Wake up. You forgot you died here."
    }
  ],
